  "title": "Clinical Psychologist / Mental Health",
  "description": "<p><strong>Who we are</strong><br /><br /><br />We are an established MOH licensed medical clinic operating for more than 7 years and looking to expand our services. We are located in CBD. We are looking for a clinical psychologist for mental health and well-being and more. Initially the candidate will be employed part-time once the patient numbers build up you will be converted to full-time. <br /><br /><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><p>Registered Clinical Psychologist <br />Experience with Mental Health Well-Being <br />Able to deal with issues such as stress, addictions (eg. alcohol, smoking, gambling) , impulsive behaviors, relationship issues, children school assessments / IQ testing, pre and post natal mood issues <br />You will be able to formulate treatment plans <br />At least 2 years of experience <br />Able to work part-time initially<br />Able to give educational talks and participate in marketing videos if required <br />Excellent communication skills<br /></p><p>Salary TBD<br />Work location: Remote or at Clinic <br />Part-time initially <br /></p>",
